gov.usgs.anss.edge

Class RunList

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.edge.RunList

  • public final class RunList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class keeps a series of runs which may be from different seednames. The starting and ending point of each run is kept. The idea is to simply add data to this class which will add the data to a run if it fits, or create new runs. After all of the runs have been created, the consolidate() method will attempt to eliminate overlapping or adjoining runs into single runs.
